{"tid":136540,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"肥完路試之後既第一堂","createTime":"2017-02-27T06:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T02:51:21.000Z","uid":7007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b8c755727e3cbc7c9ee42aa6c0257b558018c78","tid":136540,"uid":7007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:29:42.000Z","msg":"之前永孝街肥左丙部<br />\n（唔衝燈急停 頭轆踩左白界）<br />\n今次抽到油塘<br />\n新車+新師傅<br />\n上一手師傅係舊車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n5oJhix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn5oJhix.jpg&h=2bca7b01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上斜都要吊極力子+俾油<br />\n經常上三波<br />\n幾好揸<br />\n但今次換左架新車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MCVYbM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MCVYbM.jpg&h=33fe0a82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n師傅話淨吊極力子都夠<br />\n而且少左上三波<br />\n就鯉魚門道大直路先有機<br />\n好唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家揸呢種車有咩心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b8318b8504853d83a49d83803a46f6d079af82","tid":136540,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:34:15.000Z","msg":"新車好好力<br />\n聽住turbo聲簡直係一大享受"},{"pid":"d132e1741d6fdaf0ac0a5fcf10624a2e9b858249","tid":136540,"uid":78826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:39:41.000Z","msg":"舊式好揸wor 波箱位置方便 <br />\n新式入波要圾前個人"},{"pid":"01de26e49142d9fef8013cf13895053dcb15595a","tid":136540,"uid":7007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊式好揸wor 波箱位置方便 <br />\n新式入波要圾前個人</blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\n手制方便"},{"pid":"58c9807f58206ed208d4d7df4a50f12a450f4ced","tid":136540,"uid":57584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:12:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44074ce69261ad2d204eeacd97ec215c0f1eef44","tid":136540,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T09:03:22.000Z",